				<h1>Changelog (1.3 -> 1.4)</h1>
			</div>

			<div class="codestyle">
				<p>Advanced Darkness 1.4 for Minecraft 1.12.2</p>

				<p>Additions:</p>
				<li>Add configuration for causing harm in total darkness</li>
				<ul>
					<li>Add boolean for causing damage in darkness</li>
					<li>Add float for how much damage in hearts is caused</li>
					<li>Add int for game ticks between damage ticks</li>
				</ul>

				<li>Add configuration for specifying darkness on a per-dimension basis</li>
				<ul>
					<li>Add whitelist for dimensions which are always dark</li>
					<li>Add blacklist for dimensions which are never darkness</li>
					<li>Add boolean for applying darkness by default</li>
				</ul>

				<li>Add ingame configuration menu using Forge mod options</li>
			</div>


